Requirements
--------------------------

To use this program, yo need to install this packages:

- python-wxgtk2.8
- python-pyaudio
- python-numpy 
- python-scipy
- python-matplotlib

In Debian system, you can write:

	apt-get install python-wxgtk2.8 python-pyaudio python-numpy python-scipy python-matplotlib

Then, to launch the program, you can do this:

	- Give it execution permissions and then: $ ./main.py
	- Execute with: $ python main.py